room_title: Escape room "Casino Heist" by Paradox Escape Room in Phoenix
room_address: 7 E Palo Verde St #9 Gilbert, AZ 85296
room_description: When it comes to picking locks and cracking safes, you and your team are the best in the business.  You have 60 minutes to infiltrate the city's most highly guarded casino, find your way into the vault and get out with the money before law enforcement or, even worse, the casino owner's security shows up. Do you have what it takes to escape?
